<body>
    <h1>Data Collection</h1>
    <p>Honey Bear Merge only collects and stores high score data on your device. This data is stored locally and is not transmitted to any external servers or third parties. We do not collect, store, or share any other personal data or information from our users.</p>
</body>
<body>
    <h1>No Third-Party Services</h1>
    <p>Honey Bear Merge does not integrate with any third-party services or platforms that could potentially collect your data. All data, including high scores, remains on your device and is not accessible by us or any other entity.</p>
